    "Since the dtype contains types other than int, float; we need to convert those column values into proper format in order to fit the data in model."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 9,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "['job',\n",
